snippet.textDisplay: As an ethnic Chinese living in SEA, I am proud that China is hosting the winter Olympic games. US' opposition is sour grapes.  Complaints on Human rights issue in xingjang is nonsense. Hardly 0.0000000% of the people there care about the US or its antics which is declared to be America first anyway. Just let us bear that in mind and don't expect anything from the US except destruction and death like in Iraq and Afghanistan.
